intell-nextword/
├── main.py                    # FastAPI server
├── requirements.txt           # Dependencies
├── train_models.py            # To train n-gram models
└── web/
    └── index.html            # Frontend HTML  
app/
├── __init__.py               # Empty file (just to make it a Python package)
├── ngram.py                  # N-gram model implementation
├── spellchecker.py           # Spell checking functionality
└── data/                     # Your datasets and trained models
    ├── en.txt                # English corpus
    ├── hi.txt                # Hindi corpus
    ├── te.txt                # Telugu corpus
    ├── ta.txt                # Tamil corpus
    ├── kn.txt                # Kannada corpus
    ├── fr.txt                # French corpus
    ├── en_word_frequency.txt # English dictionary
    ├── hi_word_frequency.txt # Hindi dictionary
    └── ... (other language word frequency files)



  how to run the code 
  1. python train_models.py 
  2.uvicorn main:app --reload
